485
00:15:58,310 --> 00:15:59,070
Who do you love?

486
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:01,070
Who commands your desires?

487
00:16:01,850 --> 00:16:03,150
Where is your wealth stored?

488
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:04,870
What is your metric for honor?

489
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:06,150
Who is your real enemy?

490
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:07,930
And what is holding you up?

491
00:16:08,210 --> 00:16:11,210
Ghazali uses Hatim to demonstrate that 33 years

492
00:16:11,210 --> 00:16:13,570
