493
00:16:13,570 --> 00:16:14,610
walking encyclopedia.

494
00:16:14,610 --> 00:16:17,290
They were meant to produce a transformed human

495
00:16:17,290 --> 00:16:17,690
being.

496
00:16:18,090 --> 00:16:19,990
At the beginning of the story, eight benefits

497
00:16:19,990 --> 00:16:22,530
