501
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:31,490
We spend our entire lives assuming that growth

502
00:16:31,490 --> 00:16:32,530
means adding complexity.

503
00:16:33,170 --> 00:16:35,450
We gather more books, more opinions, more sophisticated

504
00:16:35,450 --> 00:16:38,470
