505
00:16:38,470 --> 00:16:39,510
information will save us.

506
00:16:39,610 --> 00:16:42,270
But Hatim's 33 years suggests the exact opposite.

507
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:44,810
What if true spiritual education is actually a

508
00:16:44,810 --> 00:16:46,450
process of aggressive subtraction?

509
00:16:47,110 --> 00:16:48,550
What if the goal isn't to build a

510
00:16:48,550 --> 00:16:51,630
more complicated mind, but to unlearn the noise

511
00:16:51,630 --> 00:16:53,570
until you are left with nothing but the

512
00:16:53,570 --> 00:16:56,590
few solid truths that can actually survive the

513
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:56,950
grave?

514
00:16:57,770 --> 00:16:59,670
Which brings us to a final thought directed

515
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:00,950
squarely at you, the listener.

516
00:17:01,470 --> 00:17:03,270
This deep dive began with a teacher asking

517
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:05,650
