518
00:17:05,650 --> 00:17:06,849
years of life and study.

519
00:17:07,109 --> 00:17:08,890
If someone asked you today to name the

520
00:17:08,890 --> 00:17:11,130
core pivots that currently define the architecture of

521
00:17:11,130 --> 00:17:12,910
your life, would you have an answer?

522
00:17:13,410 --> 00:17:15,589
And more importantly, if we apply Hatim's very

523
00:17:15,589 --> 00:17:18,510
